[Text Area]
Section=0
Page=2
Text=* Schematic File
Text=*
Text=* Syntax:
Text=* .MODEL <model name> [AKO:<reference model name>] <ModelType>
Text=* +([<parameter name>=<value>][LOT[/#][/GAUSS|/UNIFORM|/WCASE]=[<tol>[%]] |[-<low>%,<high>%]][DEV[/#][/GAUSS|/UNIFORM|/WCASE]=[<tol>[%]]...)
Text=* ModelType must be one of OPA,D,NPN,NMOS,NJF,PUL,SIN,TRN,CORE,GASFET,VSWITCH,ISWITCH,CAP,IND,RES,PNP,PMOS,PJF,DOUTPUT,DINPUT,UADC,UDAC,UGATE,UTGATE,UEFF,UGFF,UDLY,UPLD,UROM,URAM,UBGT,UIO,LPNP,NIGBT,I,V
Text=*
Text=*Examples:
Text=* .MODEL 2N2222A NPN(BF=150 IS=1E-14)
Text=* .model M1 NMOS(KP=2.5E-5 VTO=1.345 CGDO=14.67p CGBO=4.566p)
Text=* .MODEL DK D(IS=1E-18)
Text=* .model 2N2222A AKO:2N2222 NPN (BF=55 ISE=10F)
Text=* .Model BJT1 NPN (RE=12 LOT/1/GAUSS=30% DEV/2/UNIFORM=2%)
Text=*
Text=* A .cir file is typically found in the data directory
Text=*
Text=.MODEL BC847B NPN (BF=290 BR=10 CJC=1.5E-12 CJE=12E-12 FC=0.5 IKF=0.08
Text=+ IS=1.0E-14 ISE=5.0E-14 ITF=0.02 MJC=0.34 MJE=0.38 NE=1.46 NF=1.004 NR=1.0
Text=+ RB=10 RC=1 RE=0.3 TF=1.59E-9 TR=100E-9 VAF=100 VAR=10 VJC=0.6 VJE=0.73 VTF=10
Text=+ XTB=1.5 XTF=1)
Text=)
Text=
Text=
Text=.MODEL AO3422A NMOS (LEVEL=3 CBS=50E-12 CGBO=1E-11 CGDO=0.24E-9 CGSO=0.5E-9
Text=+ FC=0.5 GAMMA=0.5 IS=2.5E-14 KP=5.5 LAMBDA=0.03 MJ=0.5
Text=+ MJSW=0.38                                           ; --- Temperature ---    UO      = 600
Text=+ N=1.0 NSUB=1.0E17 PB=0.8 PHI=0.65 RD=0.035
Text=+ RDS=1E6                                              ;--- Junction RG=1.3
Text=+ RS=0.035 TOX=40E-9 VTO=1.6)
Text=)
Text=.MODEL 2N2714 NPN ()

